\c 16
\s Imikhosi emithathu emikhulu
\p
\v 1 Gcina inyanga kaAbhibhi, wenzele iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho iphasika\x + 16.8, Eks. 12.2-39. Levi 23.4.\x*, ngoba ngenyanga kaAbhibhi iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho yakukhupha eGibhithe ebusuku\x + Eks. 13.4; 34.18.\x*.
\v 2 Ngakho uzahlabela iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho iphasika, lezimvu lenkomo\x + Nani 28.19.\x*, endaweni iN\nd kosi\nd* ezayikhetha ukuthi ibeke ibizo layo khona\x + 12.5.\x*.
\v 3 Ungadli lalo isinkwa esilemvubelo. Insuku eziyisikhombisa uzakudla lalo isinkwa esingelamvubelo, isinkwa senhlupheko, ngoba waphuma elizweni leGibhithe ngokuphangisa, ukuze ukhumbule usuku lokuphuma kwakho elizweni leGibhithe zonke izinsuku zempilo yakho\x + Eks. 12.11. Isa. 52.12.\x*.
\v 4 Njalo kakungabonwa kuwe imvubelo emingceleni yonke yakho insuku eziyisikhombisa; futhi okwenyama oyihlaba kusihlwa\x + 13.7.\x* ngosuku lokuqala kakungalali ubusuku \add bonke\add* kuze kuse\x + Eks. 34.25.\x*.
\v 5 Awulakuhlaba iphasika phakathi kwaloba yiliphi lamasango akho, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunika wona,
\v 6 kodwa endaweni iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ezayikhetha ukuhlalisa ibizo layo khona, lapho uzahlabela iphasika kusihlwa, ekutshoneni kwelanga, ngesikhathi esimisiweyo sokuphuma kwakho eGibhithe\x + Eks. 12.6.\x*.
\v 7 Njalo uzalipheka, ulidlele endaweni iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ezayikhetha. Lekuseni uzaphenduka uye emathenteni akho\x + 2 Lan. 35.13.\x*.
\v 8 Insuku eziyisithupha uzakudla isinkwa esingelamvubelo\x + 16.3,4. Eks. 12.16. 13.6.\x*; langosuku lwesikhombisa kube lomhlangano onzulu eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakho; ungenzi umsebenzi\x + Levi 23.8.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Uzazibalela amaviki ayisikhombisa\x + Eks. 23.16. 34.22. Levi 23.15. Nani 28.26. Seb. 2.1.\x*. Kusukela beqalisa \add nge\add*sikela emabeleni\x + 23.25.\x* amileyo uzaqala ukubala amaviki ayisikhombisa.
\v 10 Khona uzagcinela iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho umkhosi wamaviki, umnikelo wesihle wesandla sakho, ozawunikela, njengalokhu iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ikubusisile\x + 16.17. 1 Kor. 16.2.\x*.
\v 11 Njalo uzathokoza phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, wena lendodana yakho lendodakazi yakho, lenceku yakho lencekukazi yakho, lomLevi ophakathi kwamasango akho, lowezizweni, lentandane, lomfelokazi, abaphakathi kwakho, endaweni iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ezayikhetha ukuhlalisa ibizo layo khona\x + 12.7,12,18; 14.26; 16.14.\x*.
\v 12 Uzakhumbula-ke ukuthi wawuyisigqili eGibhithe. Njalo uzagcina njalo wenze lezizimiso\x + 5.15.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Umkhosi wamadumba uzazigcinela wona insuku eziyisikhombisa, ekubutheleni kwakho ebaleni lakho lokubhulela lesikhamelweni sakho sewayini\x + Eks. 23.16. Levi 23.34.\x*.
\v 14 Njalo uzathaba emkhosini wakho, wena lendodana yakho lendodakazi yakho, lenceku yakho lencekukazi yakho, lomLevi, lowezizweni, lentandane, lomfelokazi, abaphakathi kwamasango akho\x + 16.11. Neh. 8.9-12.\x*.
\v 15 Insuku eziyisikhombisa uzayigcinela iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho umkhosi, endaweni iN\nd kosi\nd* ezayikhetha; ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho izakubusisa kuzo zonke izithelo zakho lemsebenzini wonke wezandla zakho. Ngakho uzathokoza ngoqotho\x + Levi 23.39.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Kathathu ngomnyaka wonke owesilisa wakho uzabonakala phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho endaweni ezayikhetha, ngomkhosi wesinkwa esingelamvubelo, langomkhosi wamaviki, langomkhosi wamadumba\x + Eks. 23.14,17. 34.23.\x*. Njalo kayikubonakala phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* engaphathanga lutho\x + Eks. 23.14,15.\x*;
\v 17 ngulowo lalowo ngokwesipho sesandla sakhe, njengesibusiso seN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, ekunike sona\x + 16.10.\x*.
\s Abahluleli lomsebenzi wabo
\p
\v 18 Abahluleli\x + 1.16. 2 Lan. 19.5,8.\x* lezinduna uzazibekela bona emasangweni akho wonke, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunika wona, phakathi kwezizwe zakho, ukuthi bahlulele abantu ngesahlulelo esilungileyo\x + 20.5,8,9. 29.10. 31.28. 1 Lan. 23.4. 26.29. Nani 11.16. Josh. 1.10.\x*.
\v 19 Ungaphambuli isahlulelo\x + Eks. 23.2,6. 24.17. Levi 19.15.\x*, ungakhangeli ubuso\x + 1.17.\x*, ungemukeli isipho, ngoba isipho siphumputhekisa amehlo abahlakaniphileyo, siphambula amazwi abalungileyo\x + Eks. 23.8. Tshu.7.7.\x*.
\v 20 Ukulunga, ukulunga uzakunxwanela, ukuze uphile, udle ilifa lelizwe iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunika lona.
\p
\v 21 Ungazihlanyeleli isixuku saloba yisiphi isihlahla eduze kwelathi leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho\x + 1 Kho. 14.15. 16.33. 2 Kho. 13.6. 17.16. 21.3. 2 Lan. 33.3. Eks. 34.13.\x*, ozazenzela lona\x + 1 Kho. 14.15. 16.33. 2 Kho. 13.6. 17.16. 21.3. 2 Lan. 33.3. Eks. 34.13.\x*.
\v 22 Njalo ungazimiseli insika eyisithombe, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho eyizondayo.